      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a solid foundation for someone willing to put in some work. While the engine is operational and the car is drivable, it requires a comprehensive tune-up and likely some suspension work to return to peak performance. The exterior shows its age with noticeable paint fading and some minor surface rust, and the interior exhibits significant wear on the upholstery. It is a functional driver that would greatly benefit from cosmetic and mechanical attention.",
