    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it spotless, and it drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
