    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014it's been pampered since day one and is in truly flawless condition. No scratches, no spills, and it drives like a total dream! I\u2019ve taken a lot of pride in keeping it spotless, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will love it just as much as I have. You\u2019ve gotta see this one in person to believe how clean it is!",
      "price": 43900.0,
